member.name: IObjectWithProgID.GetProgID
member.summary: Retrieves the ProgID associated with an object.
member.param: A pointer to a string that, when this method returns successfully, contains the ProgID.
member.returns: If this method succeeds, it returns S_OK. Otherwise, it returns an HRESULT error code.

member.name: IObjectWithProgID.SetProgID
member.summary: Sets the ProgID of an object.
member.param: A pointer to a string that contains the new ProgID.
member.returns: If this method succeeds, it returns S_OK. Otherwise, it returns an HRESULT error code.

member.name: IObjectWithProgID
member.summary: Exposes methods that provide access to the ProgID associated with an object.
